Class RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfgDefn

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.admin.AbstractManagedObjectDefinition<C,S>
      • org.opends.server.admin.ManagedObjectDefinition<RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfgClient,RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfg>
        • org.opends.server.admin.std.meta.RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfgDefn

  • public final class RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfgDefn
extends ManagedObjectDefinition<RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfgClient,RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfg>
    An interface for querying the Request Filtering QOS Policy managed object definition meta information.

    The Request Filtering QOS Policy is used to define the type of requests allowed by the server.
